rows.label: qst500202_msg0001
rows.name: View from here is very grand!

rows.label: qst500202_msg0002
rows.name:
Foorara not see such wonderful
view before in all of life!

rows.label: qst500202_msg0003
rows.name:
Foorara know what friends thinking.
Life of Foorara not very long
yet. But that beside point.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0004
rows.name:
Watching people of Gula from here,
Foorara think they generally too
calm and relax for their own good.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0005
rows.name:
That because Gula people born in
lovely land of plenty of food and
nature and not much problems.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0006
rows.name:
There was war at one point,
but that no change basic
nature of people much.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0007
rows.name:
Foorara know what friends thinking.
Nopon who only alive for five years
should not make judgment about life.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0008
rows.name:
Anyway, Foorara feeling hungry now.
Want to gorge self on mushroom.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0009
rows.name:
Voltis Trade Guild Walky-Walky
Guide Book say, no good try to do
anything while tum-tum is empty.

rows.label: qst500202_msg0010
rows.name:
So gorging self on mushrooms is
correct goal of Walky-Walky!

rows.label: qst500202_msg0011
rows.name:
Anyway, maybe we meet
again. Best of luck!
